Messages.Value: Thank you for calling the travel agency, my name is Liam Johnson. How can I assist you today?
Hi Liam, my name is Rachel Brown and I'm having some issues with my travel plans. I recently booked a trip to Los Angeles from New York City and I need some assistance with my bookings.
Hi Rachel, I'm sorry to hear that you're having some issues. Can you please tell me more about the problem you're facing?
Yes Liam, I had to cancel my flight due to some personal issues but I didn't get any refund for the same.
I completely understand why you would be frustrated with that Rachel. Can you please provide me with your reservation number and the date you made the reservation?
My reservation number is XYZ123 and I made the reservation on December 20th, 2021.
Thank you for providing that information Rachel. I will look into this for you. Can you please hold while I check with the airline?
Sure, thank you very much Liam.

Thank you for holding Rachel. I spoke with the airline and unfortunately, they do not offer a refund for your canceled flight. However, they have offered  a credit for the full amount that you can use for future travel bookings. Would you like me to proceed with that?
Yes please Liam, I appreciate your help with this.
No problem, Rachel. I have processed the credit and you should receive an email shortly confirming that. Do you have any other issues that I can help you with?
No that's it for now Liam. Thank you again for your help.
You're welcome Rachel. Don't hesitate to contact us again if you need any further assistance. Have a great day!
